        "text": "If you’re wondering ‘Which is the best heating oil company near me?’ look no further. We’re proud to be the country’s largest heating oil supplier, working up and down the country to keep you warm, safe and happy all year round.\n\nWith a team of over 2,500 heating oil experts dotted across the UK, 94 depots and 900 tankers in tow, you know you can always rely on us to be on your doorstep. So we may be large in numbers, but we’re local at heart.\n\nAnd that’s just one of the reasons so many of our customers sing our praises on Trustpilot.\n\nWith Certas Energy, you always know you’re getting a fair, honest and competitively priced fuel oil all year round. We cut out the middleman so you can come direct to us, and you won’t stumble across any hidden heating oil delivery charges.\n\nPlus with our reliable heating oil service, different delivery service options and a range of ways to pay, you can always count on us.\n\nSafety is our #1 priority. From delivering your heating oil in the safest way possible, to checking over your tank before we top it up, our drivers are always dedicated to keeping you safe.\n\nAnd what’s more, all our drivers are safety trained, and our OFTEC registered engineers can help you with boiler maintenance, repairs and replacements too."
